flowchart TD
  Trigger["Bad CLI, Action, docs, or exporter release"] --> Classify{"Risk type"}
  Classify -- "secret leak" --> RemoveArtifacts["Remove or revoke exposed artifacts"]
  Classify -- "invalid BOM output" --> RestorePrevious["Restore previous package or action tag"]
  Classify -- "permission escalation" --> PinSafe["Pin or republish least-privilege action"]
  Classify -- "contract drift" --> PatchDocs["Patch source-of-truth docs and examples"]
  RemoveArtifacts --> Notice["Publish user-facing notice"]
  RestorePrevious --> Notice
  PinSafe --> Notice
  PatchDocs --> Notice
  Notice --> Verify["Run validation against previous and fixed behavior"]
